(5130, 'Vonogastric 10 mg 20 oral dis. tabs.', 'فونوجاستريك 10 مجم 20 قرص', '', '124', 'Vonoprazan', 'P & c labs', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Peptic ulcer.potassium-competitive acid blocker', '10 mg', 'Vonoprazan is indicated for the following conditions: 
